  "description": "A colonial organism singing as one. Bio exciter at 0.6 mix with brightness at 1500 Hz creates a mid-frequency texture layer. LFO1 at 0.043 Hz and LFO2 at 0.029 Hz — two coprime rates that never synchronize, modeling the independent zooids of a siphonophore colony operating in loose coordination. Cave body adds the colony's shared resonant cavity. Each zooid acts independently but the colony produces a unified song.",
