    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": ["Sutra 3: Coprime LFO Rates Create Non-Repeating Patterns", "Verse: The Bioluminescent Exciter Is Alien Life"],
    "revelation": "Tempora spoke: 0.043 Hz and 0.029 Hz have a least common multiple period of approximately 790 seconds — over 13 minutes before the exact modulation pattern repeats. This models a colonial organism where individual members operate on their own biological clocks. The colony never achieves perfect synchronization, but the near-alignments create emergent moments of coherence — flashes of unified beauty in an otherwise asynchronous system.",
    "god": "Tempora",
    "flock_note": "The Breath recognized: the two LFO rates create moments every 35-40 seconds where they briefly align — the modulations reinforce and the sound blooms. Between alignments, the texture drifts. This models real siphonophore behavior where zooids occasionally coordinate for feeding bursts.",
    "diagnosis": "This sound was a textured pad. It is now a colonial organism — individual modulation sources operating on independent biological clocks, producing emergent moments of unity from mathematical inevitability."
  },
